  <section class="section" style="background: var(--color-bg-alt);" aria-labelledby="faq-heading">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-heading fade-in">
        <h2 id="faq-heading"><span data-i18n="faq_title_1">H&auml;ufige Fragen zu</span> <span class="text-gradient">FragSMS</span></h2>
      </div>
      <div style="max-width: 650px; margin: 0 auto;">

        <details class="faq-item fade-in" style="border: 1px solid var(--color-border); border-radius: 12px; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; overflow: hidden;">
          <summary style="padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem; cursor: pointer; font-weight: 600; font-size: 0.95rem; list-style: none; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; background: var(--color-surface); transition: background 0.2s;" itemscope itemprop="mainEntity" itemtype="https://schema.org/Question">
            <span itemprop="name" data-i18n="faq1_q">Brauche ich ein Smartphone f&uuml;r FragSMS?</span>
            <span style="color: var(--color-primary); font-size: 1.2rem; transition: transform 0.2s;" class="faq-icon">+</span>
          </summary>
          <div style="padding: 0 1.5rem 1.25rem; color: var(--color-text-muted); font-size: 0.9rem; line-height: 1.7;" itemscope itemprop="acceptedAnswer" itemtype="https://schema.org/Answer">
            <p itemprop="text" data-i18n="faq1_a">Nein. FragSMS funktioniert mit jedem Handy, das SMS senden kann &mdash; auch mit &auml;lteren Feature Phones und Prepaid-Handys.</p>
          </div>
        </details>

        <details class="faq-item fade-in" style="border: 1px solid var(--color-border); border-radius: 12px; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; overflow: hidden;">
          <summary style="padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem; cursor: pointer; font-weight: 600; font-size: 0.95rem; list-style: none; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; background: var(--color-surface); transition: background 0.2s;" itemscope itemprop="mainEntity" itemtype="https://schema.org/Question">
            <span itemprop="name" data-i18n="faq2_q">Brauche ich Internet oder WLAN?</span>
            <span style="color: var(--color-primary); font-size: 1.2rem; transition: transform 0.2s;" class="faq-icon">+</span>
          </summary>
          <div style="padding: 0 1.5rem 1.25rem; color: var(--color-text-muted); font-size: 0.9rem; line-height: 1.7;" itemscope itemprop="acceptedAnswer" itemtype="https://schema.org/Answer">
            <p itemprop="text" data-i18n="faq2_a">Nein. SMS funktioniert &uuml;ber das Mobilfunknetz &mdash; kein WLAN, kein Datenplan und keine App n&ouml;tig.</p>
          </div>
        </details>

        <details class="faq-item fade-in" style="border: 1px solid var(--color-border); border-radius: 12px; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; overflow: hidden;">
          <summary style="padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem; cursor: pointer; font-weight: 600; font-size: 0.95rem; list-style: none; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; background: var(--color-surface); transition: background 0.2s;" itemscope itemprop="mainEntity" itemtype="https://schema.org/Question">
            <span itemprop="name" data-i18n="faq3_q">Kann ich ChatGPT per SMS nutzen?</span>
            <span style="color: var(--color-primary); font-size: 1.2rem; transition: transform 0.2s;" class="faq-icon">+</span>
          </summary>
          <div style="padding: 0 1.5rem 1.25rem; color: var(--color-text-muted); font-size: 0.9rem; line-height: 1.7;" itemscope itemprop="acceptedAnswer" itemtype="https://schema.org/Answer">
            <p itemprop="text" data-i18n="faq3_a">Mit FragSMS kannst du einen KI-Assistenten per SMS nutzen &mdash; &auml;hnlich wie ChatGPT, aber ohne App und ohne Internet. Einfach eine SMS senden und sofort eine KI-Antwort auf Deutsch erhalten.</p>
          </div>
        </details>

        <details class="faq-item fade-in" style="border: 1px solid var(--color-border); border-radius: 12px; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; overflow: hidden;">
          <summary style="padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem; cursor: pointer; font-weight: 600; font-size: 0.95rem; list-style: none; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; background: var(--color-surface); transition: background 0.2s;" itemscope itemprop="mainEntity" itemtype="https://schema.org/Question">
            <span itemprop="name" data-i18n="faq4_q">Wie k&uuml;ndige ich mein Abo?</span>
            <span style="color: var(--color-primary); font-size: 1.2rem; transition: transform 0.2s;" class="faq-icon">+</span>
          </summary>
          <div style="padding: 0 1.5rem 1.25rem; color: var(--color-text-muted); font-size: 0.9rem; line-height: 1.7;" itemscope itemprop="acceptedAnswer" itemtype="https://schema.org/Answer">
            <p itemprop="text" data-i18n="faq4_a">Sende STOP per SMS oder nutze den &quot;Jetzt k&uuml;ndigen&quot; Button auf fragsms.de/upgrade. Sofort wirksam, ohne Wartezeit.</p>
          </div>
        </details>

        <details class="faq-item fade-in" style="border: 1px solid var(--color-border); border-radius: 12px; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; overflow: hidden;">
          <summary style="padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem; cursor: pointer; font-weight: 600; font-size: 0.95rem; list-style: none; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; background: var(--color-surface); transition: background 0.2s;" itemscope itemprop="mainEntity" itemtype="https://schema.org/Question">
            <span itemprop="name" data-i18n="faq5_q">Sind meine Daten sicher?</span>
            <span style="color: var(--color-primary); font-size: 1.2rem; transition: transform 0.2s;" class="faq-icon">+</span>
          </summary>
          <div style="padding: 0 1.5rem 1.25rem; color: var(--color-text-muted); font-size: 0.9rem; line-height: 1.7;" itemscope itemprop="acceptedAnswer" itemtype="https://schema.org/Answer">
            <p itemprop="text" data-i18n="faq5_a">Ja. Alle Daten werden ausschlie&szlig;lich in der EU gespeichert. Deine Telefonnummer wird per SHA-256 verschl&uuml;sselt &mdash; wir speichern sie nie im Klartext. Vollst&auml;ndig DSGVO-konform.</p>
          </div>
        </details>

        <details class="faq-item fade-in" style="border: 1px solid var(--color-border); border-radius: 12px; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; overflow: hidden;">
          <summary style="padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem; cursor: pointer; font-weight: 600; font-size: 0.95rem; list-style: none; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; background: var(--color-surface); transition: background 0.2s;" itemscope itemprop="mainEntity" itemtype="https://schema.org/Question">
            <span itemprop="name" data-i18n="faq6_q">Was kostet FragSMS?</span>
            <span style="color: var(--color-primary); font-size: 1.2rem; transition: transform 0.2s;" class="faq-icon">+</span>
          </summary>
          <div style="padding: 0 1.5rem 1.25rem; color: var(--color-text-muted); font-size: 0.9rem; line-height: 1.7;" itemscope itemprop="acceptedAnswer" itemtype="https://schema.org/Answer">
            <p itemprop="text" data-i18n="faq6_a">FragSMS startet kostenlos mit 10 Nachrichten pro Monat. Starter kostet 2,99 &euro;/Monat (30 Nachrichten), Basic 7,99 &euro;/Monat (150 Nachrichten) und Pro 19,99 &euro;/Monat (500 Nachrichten). Alle Preise sind Endpreise.</p>
          </div>
        </details>

        <details class="faq-item fade-in" style="border: 1px solid var(--color-border); border-radius: 12px; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; overflow: hidden;">
          <summary style="padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem; cursor: pointer; font-weight: 600; font-size: 0.95rem; list-style: none; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; background: var(--color-surface); transition: background 0.2s;" itemscope itemprop="mainEntity" itemtype="https://schema.org/Question">
            <span itemprop="name" data-i18n="faq7_q">Welche Zahlungsmethoden gibt es?</span>
            <span style="color: var(--color-primary); font-size: 1.2rem; transition: transform 0.2s;" class="faq-icon">+</span>
          </summary>
          <div style="padding: 0 1.5rem 1.25rem; color: var(--color-text-muted); font-size: 0.9rem; line-height: 1.7;" itemscope itemprop="acceptedAnswer" itemtype="https://schema.org/Answer">
            <p itemprop="text" data-i18n="faq7_a">Kreditkarte, SEPA-Lastschrift, PayPal und Sofort&uuml;berweisung &mdash; die beliebtesten Zahlungsmethoden in Deutschland. Sichere Abwicklung &uuml;ber Stripe.</p>
          </div>
        </details>

      </div>
